text: Angkor Borei Commune () is a khum (commune) in Angkor Borei District, Takeo Province, Cambodia. == Administration == As of 2019, the commune has 6 phums (villages) as follows. {| class="wikitable sortable" !No. !Code !Village !Khmer |- !1 |21010101 |Kampong Luong |កំពង់ហ្លួង |- !2 |21010102 |Stueng Kambot |ស្ទឹងកំបុត |- !3 |21010103 |Prey Sambuor |ព្រៃសំបួរ |- !4 |21010104 |Tuol Sang Ka |ទួលសាំង ក |- !5 |21010105 |Tuol Sang Kha |ទួលសាំង ខ |- !6 |21010106 |Sameakki |សាមគ្គី |} == References == Category:Communes of Takeo Province Category:Angkor Borei District
